vaccineProgram.screenHeader: Please answer all questions. In addition, you will need to bring proof of occupation or priority status, which may include an employee ID card, a letter from your employer or affiliated organization or a recent pay stub.
vaccineProgram.description: Eligible 1A and 1B priority groups including frontline, high-risk healthcare workers; residents and staff in certain group living facilities; older adults; grocery workers; and first responders.
